title: "Templates command: document correct invocation syntax (positional vs --name)"
description: "pm templates save --name fails with 'Unknown option --name'. The templates subcommands use positional arguments not flags. The AGENTS.md and help text should clarify the correct syntax: pm templates save <name> [options]."
